/*
 * OpenMP directive/clause applicability through OpenMP 6.0.
 *
 * The baseline was generated from LLVM 22 OpenMP TableGen records and then
 * audited against the OpenMP 6.0 specification and November 2025 errata.
 * Historical spellings remain accepted because this parser has no versioned
 * parse mode. OpenMP 6.0 additions and compound directives apply the
 * composition rules for their specified constituent constructs; their clause
 * sets are not necessarily a mechanical union of constituent clause sets.
 */

